              "The Android system will always strive to clear as much memory as it can. So, if your activity is down to the background, and another foreground activity is demanding its share, the Android system will call "
            ],
            [
              "onTrimMemory()",
              [
                [
                  "c"
                ]
              ]
            ],
            [
              " on your activity."
            ]
          ]
